OL,3,CJersey's public spending
OL,4,C'unsustainable' warns finance panel
OL,6,FAn independent panel has warned
OL,7,FJersey's government that it is
OL,8,Fspending beyond its means and the
OL,9,Ffinancial reserves need rebuilding.
OL,11,FThe Fiscal Policy Panel (FPP) advises
OL,12,Fon the island's economy and public
OL,13,Ffinances, and plays a key role in
OL,14,FJersey's fiscal framework.
OL,16,FIt said that the current level of
OL,17,Fpublic spending is "unsustainable" and
OL,18,Fcontinues to exceed revenues, "driven
OL,19,Fprimarily by further growth in
OL,20,Fspending on health".
