OL,3,CJersey's public spending
OL,4,C'unsustainable' warns finance panel
OL,6,FThe island's reserves have been drawn
OL,7,Fon to fill the "gap between spending
OL,8,Fand revenue" and "need to be rebuilt
OL,9,Fto ensure the resilience of the
OL,10,Feconomy ... the States of Jersey needs
OL,11,Fto save more".
OL,13,FIt also said that Jersey's balance
OL,14,Fsheet "has deteriorated since COVID."
OL,16,FThe ever-growing public debt in Jersey
OL,17,Fis expected to hit #1.3 billion by
OL,18,Fnext year, the highest level ever.
