OL,3,CJersey's public spending
OL,4,C'unsustainable' warns finance panel
OL,6,FSir Jon Cunliffe, Chair of the FPP,
OL,7,Ftold ITV News: "It cannot continue to
OL,8,Fincrease in real terms every budget.
OL,10,F"If it does, other expenditure has to
OL,11,Fbe cut, other programmes have to be
OL,12,Fcut, capital investment has to be cut,
OL,13,For you have to borrow more or run the
OL,14,Freserves down".
OL,16,FThe panel also pointed to the
OL,17,F"sluggish" housing market in 2024,
OL,18,Fwith the number of transactions
OL,19,Freaching its lowest levels since 2002.
