OL,3,CJersey's public spending
OL,4,C'unsustainable' warns finance panel
OL,6,FResponding to their findings, Jersey's
OL,7,FTreasury Minister, Deputy Elaine
OL,8,FMillar, said the report "does not
OL,9,Fcontain any surprises."
OL,11,FShe added: "This Government recognises
OL,12,Fthe difficult trade-offs between
OL,13,Fdelivering essential public services,
OL,14,Finvesting in infrastructure, and
OL,15,Frebuilding reserves.
OL,17,F"This includes a recruitment and
OL,18,Fconsultancy freeze, which has already
OL,19,Fdelivered significant savings.
