OL,3,CJersey's public spending
OL,4,C'unsustainable' warns finance panel
OL,6,F"The States grant to the Social
OL,7,FSecurity Fund has been reduced on a
OL,8,Ftemporary basis while we await the
OL,9,Foutcome of the 2025 actuarial review
OL,10,Fbefore making any further longer-term
OL,11,Fdecisions. We will still be
OL,12,Fcontributing #184 million to the Fund.
OL,14,F"These actions together reflect our
OL,15,Fcommitment to the Panel's
OL,16,Frecommendation to prioritise medium-
OL,17,Fterm sustainability and resilience.
