OL,6,F"At the same time, we remain focused
OL,7,Fon protecting and investing in core
OL,8,Fpublic services ` particularly
OL,9,Fhealthcare, children's services, and
OL,10,Four ageing infrastructure ` offering a
OL,11,Fclear and practical route to improving
OL,12,Fpublic services, supporting the
OL,13,Feconomy, and maintaining Jersey's
OL,14,Fquality of life."
